high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen island.
Pick up the knife to the right of the spatula and behind the vase, on the island.
Cut the tomato on the back of the kitchen island, closest to the heads of lettuce, into slices.
Turn around and go to the cabinets under the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the front of the right cabinet, under the sink.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen island.
Pick up one of the tomato slices on the kitchen island.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave, above the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go past the stove to the garbage can on the floor, to your right.
Place the tomato slice in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife under the sink, and a warm tomato slice in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn left and move in front of the green table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Slice the tomato nearest to the upright bottle.
Turn around and move to the sink.
Put the knife in the cabinet under the sink.
Turn around and move to the green table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn left and move to the front of the stove.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right and face the trash can next to the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato slice in the microwave and put it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the side of the island with a green sponge and a knife.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Slice the red tomato  in front of the glass on the right aside of the lettuce.
Turn around and go to the left cabinet below the sink.
Place the knife in the cabinet in front of the glass.
Turn around back towards the island with the sliced tomato.
Pick up a slice of the tomato from the counter.
Turn left and go to the microwave above the stove.
Remove the slice of tomato after microwaving it.
Turn right and go to the trash can on the floor at the end of the counter.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out the heated tomato slice.
